
---

**StreamTwistGraph**  
**Description:**  
Displays live numerical streams with a twisting line effect to emphasize volatility and rate of change.

```markdown
# StreamTwistGraph - Live Data Stream Visualizer

StreamTwistGraph creates a dynamic flowing graph that twists based on directional movement and value deltas.

## Features
- Twisting animation logic  
- Scrollable timeline  
- Built with Matplotlib

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/StreamTwistGraph.git
cd StreamTwistGraph
python visualize.py
